Package com.kneelawk.graphlib.api.graph

Interface GraphView

All Known Subinterfaces:
GraphWorld
public interface GraphView
Interface that allows access to the nodes at given positions.

    • getAllGraphs

      @NotNull default @NotNull Stream<BlockGraph> getAllGraphs()
      Gets all graphs in this graph world, loading all graphs. Use with care.

      This filters out all the null graphs.

      Because this loads all graphs in the graph world, it can cause significant lag. Chances are, you actually want getLoadedGraphs().

      Returns:
      a stream of all the graphs in this graph world.

    • getLoadedGraphs

      @NotNull @NotNull Stream<BlockGraph> getLoadedGraphs()
      Gets all currently loaded graphs.
      Returns:
      all the currently loaded graphs.
